name: MazeVR
tagline: Full virtual reality game made with unity
body:
### MazeVR
MazeVR is a virtual reality maze game made for iOS and android where the objective is to find the the end of the maze under a timed environment while also trying to pick up collectibles for points. It was built using Unity and Googleâ€™s virtual reality development kit.  

### Authors and Contributors
